-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!328713~!0#focus |publisher=[[Smithsonian Institution]] |accessdate=July 29, 2018}}</ref> The artwork was donated to the School of Architecture and Allied Arts in 1984 by Hugh Klopfenstein and his wife.<ref>{{cite web |title=Campus Artworks |url=https://cpfm.uoregon.edu/sites/cpfm2.uoregon.edu/files/art_tour_updatednov2016_copy.pdf |publisher=University of Oregon |accessdate=July 29, 2018 |date=November 2016}}</ref>
